By versioning your custom Lightning web components, we can ship new features, bug fixes, and performance improvements. Where: This change applies to custom Lightning web components in Lightning Experience, Experience Builder sites, and all versions of the Salesforce mobile app. How: To specify an API version, use the `@apiVersion` decorator on your component class. Update Your Light DOM Components for Improved Slot Forwarding This change applies to custom Lightning web components in Lightning Experience, Experience Builder sites, and all versions of the Salesforce mobile app. This change also applies to Lightning web components in open source. For example: In the latest version of LWC, native and synthetic shadow slots still preserve the slot attribute.
